{"tid":1438933,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗站有人影人樣","createTime":"2019-08-10T02:52:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T02:54:02.000Z","uid":207980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f24881b39c72be07e4e7efc6c597b9c537eb497b","tid":1438933,"uid":207980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:52:29.000Z","msg":"代朋友post<br />\n<br />\n半個鐘前係元朗西鐵站，有一男一女係站內影住出入閘既人。<br />\n<br />\n我朋友擋住個樣唔俾佢影，跟住就追住背面黎影。到朋友出完閘想話佢，佢兩個調頭走。<br />\n<br />\n兩個大陸人咁款，個女人腰部仲掛住舊野，疑似walkie talkie<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2oKp2hX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2oKp2hX.png&h=f9b5eb73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如有經過大家留意一下。"},{"pid":"b3807cf5c003dd94048cded3cd5d91d9a8a43a6d","tid":1438933,"uid":267795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:53:32.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"79fdc2f7a1186439cab08384d4a827e4ba3bdfeb","tid":1438933,"uid":21275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:54:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}